MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

1985-0007. State v. Williams.

Cuyahoga App. No. 47853. On motion to set execution date. Motion granted. On motion for stay of execution of sentence pending disposition of habeas corpus actions pursuant to Atkins v. Virginia (2002), 536 U.S. 304, 122 S.Ct. 2242, 153 L.Ed.2d 335. Motion denied.
